00174         class NameGenerator
00175         {
00176         protected:
00177                 String mPrefix;
00178                 unsigned long long int mNext;
00179                 //OGRE_AUTO_MUTEX
00180         public:
00181                 NameGenerator(const NameGenerator& rhs)
00182                         : mPrefix(rhs.mPrefix), mNext(rhs.mNext) {}
00183                 
00184                 NameGenerator(const String& prefix) : mPrefix(prefix), mNext(1) {}
00185 
00187                 String generate()
00188                 {
00189                         //OGRE_LOCK_AUTO_MUTEX
00190                         std::ostringstream s;
00191                         s << mPrefix << mNext++;
00192                         return s.str();
00193                 }
00194 
00196                 void reset()
00197                 {
00198                         //OGRE_LOCK_AUTO_MUTEX
00199                         mNext = 1ULL;
00200                 }
00201 
00203                 void setNext(unsigned long long int val)
00204                 {
00205                         //OGRE_LOCK_AUTO_MUTEX
00206                         mNext = val;
00207                 }
00208 
00210                 unsigned long long int getNext() const
00211                 {
00212                         // lock even on get because 64-bit may not be atomic read
00213                         //OGRE_LOCK_AUTO_MUTEX
00214                         return mNext;
00215                 }
00216         };
